      • importInstanceResult

        void importInstanceResult(java.lang.Integer instanceNumber,
                        java.util.List<java.lang.String> instanceKey,
                        java.lang.String task,
                        int classAuto,
                        int classGold,
                        java.util.List<java.lang.Double> predictions)
        Parameters:
        instanceNumber - optional instance number when multiple instance classified, used for outputting errors/warnings
        instanceKey - list of attributes to resolve instance - foreign key to document/sentence/whatever
        task - classification task
        classAuto - classifer's predicted class
        classGold - gold standard class index
        prediction - probabilities of belonging to specified classes, if run with -distribution option. else just probability of belonging to predicted class.
